channel.title: Lil' Whitey level 2?
channel.description: Posts in the discussion thread "Lil' Whitey level 2?" - Lil' Whitey can level up?

item.title: Re: Lil' Whitey level 2?
item.content:encoded: No, unfortunitely Lil' Whitey doesn't have another level. For future reference though, you can check out the allies page, and when you click on an ally it will give you all the info, boosts, jutsu, levels (and how to obtain them), drops and more, so check it out.

item.title: Lil' Whitey level 2?
item.content:encoded: hey, i was wondering that since almost all characters have a level 2 form, including all bruce jr and meatballs, if Lil' Whitey could level, and if he could does anyone have any idea of where or when?
